            <title>[LUCENE-1624] Don&apos;t commit an empty segments_N when IW is opened with create=true</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/LUCENE-1624</link>
                <project id="12310110" key="LUCENE">Lucene - Core</project>
